ur.com/gallery/nusQ12s</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Wx2fSvy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/nusQ12s</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BuddyGator]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wait a minute...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/h9HmW2A</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Az5B80f.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>...son of a...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/h9HmW2A</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[IAmThe1WhoCooks]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A Puckett family birthday</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FFpOZ2c</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4lEnZYt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hi everyone, I'm MrPuckett</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zTjRKjD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Back in July I adopted Nanna from Nashville Humane - a 15 year old blind dog with terminal heart disease and a long list of other health problems. 

I'm happy to report that not only is she still alive and doing amazing, but...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sblMzWX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Today is Nanna's 16th birthday ＼(°o°)／</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3Nk6Uxt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>When she first came home I didn't think she'd be alive for 6 months. Her arthritis was so bad she could barely stand up. 

7 months later and she's walking 10 miles a week, most of her hair has grown back, and she's getting a little more cuddly every week.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1fCSHcq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's been an amazing transformation for a dog that just needed a reason to fight again.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Qz6kYzB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>With her birthday we start Puckett Week - 7 days of fundraising and a Supply Drive for domestic violence survivors facing homelessness.

Last year we raised over $30,000 worth of donations and goods right here on Imgur.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VYUtYab.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Mary Parrish Center offers free housing to survivors who are either homeless or would be homeless once leaving their abuser. 

Domestic violence is the leading cause of homelessness for women and children in America.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bb4LGG0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Many survivors face the difficult decision of staying in an abusive relationship or taking their children to a homeless shelter. 

In addition to offering free apartments, they also furnish the place, provide food, job assistance, therapy and even emergency financial assistance.

Everything a survivor needs to stay safe and start their life fresh again.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f7KG29g.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You'll see me posting about this every day this week trying to promote the Supply Drive and fundraiser. 

For Nanna's 16th birthday, I thought it would be nice for anyone who can afford it to donate $16 to the Mary Parrish Center.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zSSdb3s.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Alone we can feel unable to help or make a difference, but together we have always done amazing things. 

Let's do some more amazing things this week

Happy birthday Nanna Pants, this one's for you.

...

To donate $16 -

https://www.maryparrish.org/donate

...

If you'd like to send goods to the survivors of domestic violence at Mary Parrish -

https://www.amazon.com/hz/wishlist/ls/3USHUHIVSINQE?ref_=wl_share

...

Thank you for reading my post, I'll see everyone again tomorrow.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/FFpOZ2c</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MrPuckett]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Gods darn it</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tfQZvxe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OKpnbDm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UDjWExZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pGpQDjC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AorZiyk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/48twoGb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tfQZvxe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Morg729]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Meme dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Fb0ikFq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NhtNMJ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0G0X9q6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5cvRNOV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D6wYLbi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ug8FTe2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fXSRNgz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wcnkAoR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="htt